The concept, implementation, and commercial exploitation of collecting real-time behavioral food waste data at the EAN level, including but not limited to the approach of selling aggregated anonymous behavioral reports to food industry players (including but not limited to Danone, Nestlé, Carrefour, Leclerc, ADEME, and WWF), is the exclusive intellectual property of the Owner.

Any attempt to replicate, adapt, or commercially exploit this approach by any third party who has had access to this Software or its associated documentation shall constitute both copyright infringement and trade secret misappropriation.

